h4. Release 0.5.2 (2006-04-18)

h5. Implementation

* Transport:
  Major continued development of QxTransport, QxRequest and related classes. Greatly improved QxIframeTransport. Also there are many new examples and tests.
* Colorselector:
  Added new color selector implementation. Needs further improvements like dispatching events for buttons, ...
* Cookie Storage:
  Added some examples
* XmlHttpLoader:
  Removed old xmlhttp API from qooxdoo. Also removed DataHandling examples.
* Application:
  Moved unload handling from QxApplication to QxObjectCore.
  Removed some dependencies and made them optional for QxApplication like QxImageManager.
* Native:
  Fixed regexps of trim methods.
  Added general JavaScript generics support for older JavaScript engines like MSHTML.
* Window:
  Converted QxWindowManager from a singleton back to a normal class. Added property windowManager to QxWindows to allows the specific usage of a windowManager instance. This change makes it possible to more easily implement things like virtual desktops.
* Widget:
  Minor bugfix regarding the caching of visible children.
  Minor bugfixes to remove old states from just disabled buttons, ...
  Minor bugfixes and improvements to appearance implementation to allow the dynamic switch of appearances on not-already created widgets.
* XmlExtras:
  Minor bugfixes.
* DragAndDropManager:
  Minor bugfixes
* SelectionManager:
  Minor bugfixes
* Client:
  Added runsLocally getter.
* Icons:
  Added mimeType icons.

h5. Contributions

* Buttonpane, Clock, Frame, Splitpane, Statusbar:
  Improved by Kent Olsson

h5. Documentation

* Nothing

h5. Tools

* Generate-Dev:
  Added/Fixed many build require/post flags for new compiler in generate-dev.
* Generate:
  Build zip archive with DOS carriage returns.
  Use of "/usr/bin/env bash" instead of hard-coded path.
  Other minor improvements

h4. Release 0.5.1 (2006-02-28)

h5. Implementation

* QxDragAndDropManager:
  Moved cursor creation to seperate init method to prevent premature creation of widgets
* QxCommand:
  Fixed commands for empty shortcut
* QxLabel:
  Added text-align support
* QxTree:
  Added support for user-defined tree icons
* QxRangeManager:
  Added step property
* Minor changes: QxIframe, QxApplication
* Fixed some images

h5. Contributions

* Added scroller_olsson, splitpane_olsson

h5. Documentation

* Fixed doctype to create IE valid pages

h5. Tools

* Minor fixes for build scripts
* Fixed dependency entries

